oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Williams Compilation by Jack Spiegel (Tape 1)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording is a compilation of Hank Williams songs from Jack Spiegel of Formoso, Kansas, sent to Hank Snow. The tape is not dated. Included in the tape's box are two pieces of cardboard inserts with a handwritten song list and a note that this is tape one. The inserts state there was supposed to be a second side but no such side exists, the tape only has one side. This tape is thirty-eight of an unidentified number of tapes.
